Uses of Package
com.cloudera.data

Packages that use com.cloudera.data
com.cloudera.data Provides interfaces and classes for reading and writing datasets. 
com.cloudera.data.filesystem Provides a dataset implementation for Hadoop filesystems, like HDFS. 
com.cloudera.data.impl Provides internal implementation classes that are not part of the public API, and which are not published in the Javadoc. 
com.cloudera.data.partition Provides common implementations of FieldPartitioner.
